data.description: Contentment in Clayton!  Welcome Home to this custom built Ranch style home featuring 3 Bedrooms and 2 1/2 Bathrooms.  This Rancher sits on 1.2 peaceful acres with a backyard oasis featuring a very large Saltwater Inground Pool that features a Stone Waterfall and a large Pond that has its own custom footbridge.  This home offers a living room (sunken with a Brick Fireplace), a dining room, an eat in kitchen, a wet bar area with a serving window for guest in the dining area, an office space, an all season room with wall to wall windows,  a full basement with a gas insert fireplace and a back porch area with an extendable awning to enjoy those New Jersey seasons.  All three bedrooms have hard wood flooring and the Master Bedroom Features a master En-suite and sitting room with his and her closet space.   This home also offers Solar Panels to give you efficient living!  Schedule your appointment today!!!
